(33, 1, 'After pranksters used Google Map Maker to draw an <a href="http://thenextweb.com/google/2015/04/24/theres-an-android-peeing-on-apple-on-google-maps-and-we-cant-figure-out-why/">Android peeing on an Apple Logo</a> and engage in other acts of spammy vandalism, Google <a href="https://productforums.google.com/forum/#!category-topic/map-maker/news-and-announcements/crFEbGXJ-HI">has announced</a> that it will temporarily shut down its online map editor while it rethinks its approval process.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHere is the screen that i have experienced few moments ago.\r\n\r\n<img class=" aligncenter" src="http://i.imgur.com/Zk2vRS7.png" alt="" width="1366" height="768" />\r\n\r\nAt the same time, i can able to surf few of the local address of mine.\r\n\r\nI am not sure about the exact reason. However i can advice to surf over few official releases\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone" src="http://i.imgur.com/V0VgvjZ.png" alt="" width="1366" height="768" />', 'Google Maps Marker Shutsdown temporarily starting from 12th may 2015', 'publish', 'google-maps-marker-shutsdown-temporarily-starting-from-12th-may-2015', '2015-06-17 16:27:34', '2015-06-17 16:27:34'),
