(189, 1, 'Hello, Guys.\n\nWe all know the importance of <strong>JQuery</strong> (though Angular rocks). I can say that JQuery is the step one should learn to have his things done.\n\nTrust me, its simple like air / i can assure that you will love the way i explain you(might be little childish).\n\nThe simple step i would say is like this\n\n<strong>1. Include the Library</strong>\n\n<strong>2. Define the Input</strong>\n\n<strong>3. Detect the Input Action - Trigger</strong>\n\n<strong>4. Do some operation for Input </strong>\n\n<strong>5. Define the Output</strong>\n\n<strong>6. Show your Output </strong>\n\nAll the steps can be a single line or more\n\nLet''s Begin\n\n<strong>Step 1 : </strong>\n\n<strong>     Include the Library</strong>\n\nWhy include ?\n\nBecause you don''t want to write the basic function.\n\nDo you want to do write your own ?\n\nThen\n<pre class="lang:default decode:true ">&lt;script&gt;\n\nWrite all your Basic-Mid-Hard functions here\n\n&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\n&nbsp;\n\nElse, Your want to be <strong>Smart enough ?</strong>\n\nThen just include the Library in a single line\n<pre class="lang:default decode:true ">&lt;script scr="library.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\n&nbsp;\n\nThe <em>library.js</em> is the file which is written by some good folks, It would have some hundreds of functions\n\nYou can include it directly by globally available CDN or download it from there ;)\n\nI too provide something <a href="http://www.sysaxiom.com/api/jquery.min.js" target="_blank">http://www.sysaxiom.com/api/jquery.min.js</a>\n\nSo, Inclusion of the library could be in a single line as i said\n<pre class="lang:default decode:true ">&lt;script src="sysaxiom.com/api/jquery.min.js&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</pre>\n<strong>Step 2 :</strong>\n\n<strong>     Define the Input</strong>\n\nYou can define the input / refer the input by some <strong>id</strong> or <strong>class</strong>\n\nDefine by id could be Something like\n\n[php]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[/php]\n\nDefine by class could be Something like\n\n[php]\n\n&lt;input type="text" class="MyInput"&gt;\n\nor\n\n&lt;div class="MyInput"&gt;\n\nor\n\nOption Select or Radio Button or Checkbox or Submit or anything you wish\n\n[/php]\n\nSo, coming to the point. Defining the input it would be\n\n[php]\n\n&lt;div id=''''MyTrigger"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n\n[/php]\n\n<strong>Step 3 :</strong>\n\n<strong>     Detect the Input Action - Trigger</strong>\n\nYou can detect the Input Action, Really many actions are there\n\nLike <strong>Click, Change, Hover, MouseIn, MouseOut</strong> and loads\n\nLet''s detect the input with the click action\n\n[php]\n\n&lt;script&gt;\n\n$("#MyTrigger").click(function(){  //Here we can assure that that id with MyTrigger is clicked  })\n\n&lt;/script&gt;\n\n[/php]\n\n<strong>Step 4 :</strong>\n\n<strong>    Do some operation for Input </strong>\n\nWhat Operation shall we do at this time ???\n\nAnything that you like\n\nBasic - <em>Do some 1+1 or simply smile</em>\n\nMid - <em>Do some ajax call</em>\n\nExp - <em>I really don''t know, it can be anything that you wish</em>\n\nAhm, Let''s say what happened i.e., Input is received\n\nIt can be said by\n\n<strong>Developer''s Way</strong> - Console or <strong>People''s Way</strong> - Towards the html page\n\nNote : If we follow the first one, we don''t wan''t to define the output or show output as we are outputting the information in the place which is already defined.\n\nIt is not a big deal, just a single line as i said.\n\n[php]\n\nconsole.log("Boss !!! We got the Input");\n\n[/php]\n\n<strong>5. Define the Output</strong>\n\nIf you are at this step then it is sure that you want to know/follow the People''s way\n\nHere''s how we Define the Output Section\n\n[php]\n\n&lt;div id="MyResult"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n\n[/php]\n\n<strong>6. Show your Output </strong>\n\nAnd Showing the output toward html is as simple like this\n\n[php]\n\n$("#MyResult").html("MyTrigger is Clicked");\n\n[/php]\n\nFiddle Created for This Demo\n\n1. Console Output -\n\n[iframe src="http://jsfiddle.net/allaudeen/jqq1kdon/embedded/" width="100%" height="500"]\n\n2. HTML Output -\n\n[iframe src="http://jsfiddle.net/allaudeen/4712v36u/embedded/" width="100%" height="500"]', 'How Cute the Jquery is ! With Basic Operation which is lovable - Story Version', 'inherit', '96-autosave-v1', '2015-09-01 10:04:45', '2015-09-01 10:04:45'),
